Title: Permits psychologists to form limited liability companies
Summary: Permits psychologists to form limited liability companies.
LawCode: Amd §§1203, 1207 & 1301, Lim Lil L; amd §1503, BC L; amd §§121-1500 & 121-1502, Partn L; amd §2801, Pub Health L; amd §6530, Ed L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the limited liability company law, the business corporation law, the partnership law, the public health law and the education law, in relation to allowing psychologists licensed under title VIII, article 153 of the education law to form limited liability companies
